## Limitations

The analysis is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the issue. The data is limited to the viewpoints expressed in the sources, which may not fully represent the complexity of inequality in global cities. Additionally, the lack of recent empirical data limits the ability to provide a comprehensive analysis of current trends. Further research and data collection are necessary to gain a more nuanced understanding of the issue.